#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:133
msgid ""
"For web UI users, when opening the web UI, you will first be directed to the"
" login page. After logging in, you can use the web UI normally."
msgstr "对于 Web UI 的用户，在打开 Web UI 时，将首先跳转到登录页面。登录后，就可以正常使用Web UI 的功能。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:136
