#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:269
msgid ""
"Auto-generated secrets are written once and reused on subsequent restarts, "
"so existing JWTs and encrypted API keys keep working across restarts. In a "
"distributed deployment (supervisor + workers), make sure all processes that "
"run the RESTful API share the same ``XINFERENCE_HOME`` (or set the same "
"explicit environment variables), so they agree on the same secrets and "
"database."
msgstr ""
"自动生成的密钥只会写入一次，并在后续重启时复用，因此已签发的 JWT 和已加密的 API Key 在重启后仍然可用。在分布式部署（supervisor "
"+ worker）中，请确保所有运行 RESTful API 的进程共享同一个 ``XINFERENCE_HOME``\\ "
"（或者设置相同的显式环境变量），以便它们使用相同的密钥和数据库。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:277
msgid "Advanced-system permissions"
msgstr "高级系统权限"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:278
msgid ""
"The advanced system uses the same permission names as the simple system "
"(``models:list``, ``models:read``, ``models:register``, "
"``models:unregister``, ``models:start``, ``models:stop``, ``admin``), plus "
"additional scopes for managing the advanced system itself:"
msgstr ""
"高级系统使用与简单系统相同的权限名称（``models:list``、``models:read``、``models:register``、``models:unregister``、``models:start``、``models:stop``、``admin``），并额外提供了一些用于管理高级系统本身的权限："

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:283
msgid ""
"``keys:create``: Permission to create API keys (for oneself, or for others "
"when combined with ``keys:manage``)."
msgstr "``keys:create``：创建 API Key 的权限（为自己创建；若与 ``keys:manage`` 结合，也可为他人创建）。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:284
msgid ""
"``keys:manage``: Permission to list, update, delete, and reveal any user's "
"API keys."
msgstr "``keys:manage``：列出、更新、删除以及查看任意用户 API Key 的权限。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:285
msgid ""
"``users:manage``: Permission to create, update, delete users, and manage "
"their permissions."
msgstr "``users:manage``：创建、更新、删除用户以及管理其权限的权限。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:286
msgid ""
"``cache:list`` / ``cache:delete``: Permissions to list/delete cached model "
"files."
msgstr "``cache:list`` / ``cache:delete``：列出/删除已缓存模型文件的权限。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:287
msgid ""
"``virtualenv:list`` / ``virtualenv:delete``: Permissions to list/delete per-"
"model virtual environments."
msgstr "``virtualenv:list`` / ``virtualenv:delete``：列出/删除单个模型虚拟环境的权限。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:288
#, fuzzy
msgid "``admin``: Administrators have all of the above."
msgstr "``admin``: 管理员拥有所有接口的权限。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:290
msgid ""
"A caller may only grant permissions they themselves hold — for example, a "
"user with only ``users:manage`` cannot grant ``admin`` to someone else."
msgstr "调用者只能授予自己拥有的权限——例如，只拥有 ``users:manage`` 权限的用户不能将 ``admin`` 权限授予他人。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:294
msgid "Login and API-key usage"
msgstr "登录与 API Key 使用方式"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:295
msgid ""
"Login and API-key usage (signin, ``--api-key``, ``Authorization: Bearer`` "
"header, OpenAI-SDK compatibility) work the same way as described in the "
"`Usage`_ section above for the simple system."
msgstr ""
"登录与 API Key 的使用方式（登录、``--api-key``、``Authorization: Bearer`` 请求头、与 OpenAI "
"SDK 的兼容性）与上文简单系统 `Usage`_ 一节中描述的方式相同。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:300
msgid "Managing users and API keys"
msgstr "管理用户和 API Key"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:301
msgid ""
"Once logged in as a user with the ``users:manage`` and/or ``keys:manage`` "
"permission (the bootstrap ``admin`` account has both), you can manage users "
"and API keys through REST endpoints under ``/v1/admin``, for example:"
msgstr ""
"以拥有 ``users:manage`` 和/或 ``keys:manage`` 权限的用户登录后（初始的 ``admin`` "
"账号同时拥有这两项权限），即可通过 ``/v1/admin`` 下的 REST 接口管理用户和 API Key，例如："

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:319
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Other supported endpoints include listing/updating/deleting users "
"(``/v1/admin/users``, ``/v1/admin/users/{user_id}``), changing a user's "
"password (``/v1/admin/users/{user_id}/password``), and listing, updating, "
"deleting, and revealing API keys (``/v1/admin/keys``, "
"``/v1/admin/keys/{key_id}``, ``/v1/admin/keys/{key_id}/reveal``)."
msgstr ""
"其他受支持的接口还包括：列出/更新/删除用户（``/v1/admin/users``、``/v1/admin/users/{user_id}``）、修改用户密码（``/v1/admin/users/{user_id}/password``），以及列出、更新、删除和查看"
" API "
"Key（``/v1/admin/keys``、``/v1/admin/keys/{key_id}``、``/v1/admin/keys/{key_id}/reveal``）。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:326
msgid "Behavior notes"
msgstr "行为说明"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:329
msgid "Permission changes take effect without re-login"
msgstr "权限变更无需重新登录即可生效"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:330
msgid ""
"Route scope checks read the user's **current** permissions from the database"
" on every request, not the scopes baked into the JWT at login. Granting or "
"revoking a permission takes effect on the user's next API call — no re-login"
" required. This applies to JWT-based browser sessions; API keys are also "
"live-read (they always have been)."
msgstr ""
"路由的权限检查会在每次请求时从数据库读取用户**当前**的权限，而不是使用登录时固化在 JWT 中的权限。授予或撤销权限会在用户下一次 API "
"调用时立即生效——无需重新登录。这一点适用于基于 JWT 的浏览器会话；API Key 一直以来也是实时读取权限的。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:337
msgid "Configurable access-token lifetime"
msgstr "可配置的访问令牌有效期"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:338
msgid ""
"The access-token lifetime defaults to 30 minutes and can be overridden with "
"the ``XINFERENCE_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES`` environment variable:"
msgstr ""
"访问令牌的有效期默认为 30 分钟，可以通过 ``XINFERENCE_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES`` 环境变量覆盖："

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:345
msgid ""
"A shorter lifetime shrinks the token-theft window. The refresh token "
"lifetime is 7 days and is not currently configurable."
msgstr "更短的有效期可以缩小令牌被盗用的时间窗口。刷新令牌的有效期为 7 天，目前尚不可配置。"

#: ../../../Users/oliver/Documents/Xorbits/inference/.claude/worktrees/xinference-builtin-database-355e03/doc/source/user_guide/auth_system.rst:349
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr "反馈"

